data.description: Enchanting architecture awaits you in every aspect of this Historic home in the heart of Decatur.  Flourishing with rich history this 2 story home is referred to as the Cortner House and dates back to 1908.  It is built of stone and has a gabled tile roof.  Some of the exquisite features of the home are the two stone fireplaces, archways and the rooftop terrace from the master suite where you can enjoy the sunrise or sunset. Enjoy a cup of coffee and your plants in the solarium.  There is also a stone guest house, large gazebo and fishpond in the back to relax and great for entertaining. This home is built on 7 lots. Now is the time for you to make this Iconic home yours!!!
